Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
setWhatIfLoadType(25.10)                              setWhatIfLoadType(25.10)

Name
       setWhatIfLoadType

Syntax
        setWhatIfLoadType

       <blackBoxCellName>

       [-port <inputPortName>]

       [-lib <libName>]

       -cell <libraryCellName>

       [-inputPin <libraryInputPin>]

       [-multiply_by <value>]

       Specifies  that  the load on any input or any inout what-if port should
       be the same as that of the specified library input or inout pin.

Parameters
       <blackBoxCellName>
              Specifies the name of the blackbox or blackblob cell.

       -cell library<CellName>
              Specifies the name of the cell from which the load value will be
              picked.

       -inputPin <libraryInputPin>
              The library cell input or inout pin whose source  arcs  will  be
              used for setting the load on the port.

              Default:  If  this  parameter is not specified, the software se-
              lects an input or inout pin automatically.

       -lib <libName>
              Specifies the name of the timing library from which  the  speci-
              fied cell will be picked.

              Default: The library is selected automatically based on the cur-
              rent context.

       -multiply_by <value>
              Specifies the load value multiplication factor. The applied load
              on  the blackbox or blackblob is equal to the load of the speci-
              fied cell pin multiplied by this factor.

              This parameter takes an integer or floating point value.

              <Default>: If no value is specified, the  multiplication  factor
              is set to 1.

       -port <inputPortName>
              Specifies the input or inout port of the blackbox or blackblob.

              Default:  If  no  port  is specified, the load is applied to all
              ports.

Examples
       The following command sets the load  on  the  input_Port1  of  blackbox
       Blackbox1  to the same as that on input pin Pin_A1 of cell bufx1 of li-
       brary library_DelayLogic.

       setWhatIfLoadType Blackbox1 -port input_Port1  -lib  library_DelayLogic
       -cell bufx1 -inputPin Pin_A1

